high_descs: Turn around, go to the counter with a toaster to the left of the fridge
Pick up the knife from the counter
Turn around and walk across to the white table
Slice the cabbage on the table
Go back to the counter with the toaster
Put the knife on the counter
Turn around and go back to the table with the cut cabbage
Pick a cabbage slice up from the table
Go to the fridge
Chill the cabbage slice for a few seconds and take it out of the fridge
Go back to the counter
Place the cabbage slice in on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled cabbage slice on the counter

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter with the toaster on it.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the white table.
Cut the lettuce on the white table.
Turn around and go back to the toaster.
Put the knife on the counter to the right of the toaster.
Turn around and go back to the white table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the table.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Chill the slice of lettuce in the fridge and pick it back up.
Turn left and go to the toaster on the counter.
Put the slice of lettuce on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of lettuce on the counter in front of the toaster.

high_descs: Turn around and step forward and turn left and step forward to face the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and cross the room to face the lettuce on the right end of the white table.
Cut the lettuce on the white table into slices.
Turn around and walk forward to face the counter.
Place the knife on the counter.
Turn around and cross the room to face the lettuce on the right end of the white table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the counter.
Turn around and cross the room to face the fridge.
Cool the lettuce slice in the fridge and remove it.
Step left to face the counter.
Place the lettuce slice on the counter.
anns.task_desc: TO cool a lettuce slice and place it on the counter to the left of the fridge.
